# S3 state bucket uses SSE-S3 (AES256) instead of KMS CMK
# KMS CMK adds operational risk for Terraform state - if key is deleted, state is unrecoverable
AVD-AWS-0132
# SQS DLQ uses AWS managed key (alias/aws/sqs) instead of CMK
# DLQ for Lambda error capture - AWS managed encryption is sufficient at pilot stage
AVD-AWS-0135
